OL,3,CTrees in need of 'urgent attention' in
OL,4,Cpark where man was killed
OL,6,FGranada Reports Correspondent Mel
OL,7,FBarham met with Fiona in the park
OL,8,Fwhere her husband died five years ago.
OL,10,FA widow whose husband was killed by a
OL,11,Ffalling tree branch in a park, says
OL,12,Fpeople are still at risk - with some
OL,13,Ftrees needing urgent attention.
OL,15,FChristopher Hall died from multiple
OL,16,Finjuries while walking his dog in
OL,17,FCarrs Park in Wilmslow in August 2020.
