OL,3,CTrees in need of 'urgent attention' in
OL,4,Cpark where man was killed
OL,6,FThe same tree - which was 130-years-
OL,7,Fold - had already shed another large
OL,8,Flimb less than one year before the
OL,9,Ffatal incident.
OL,11,FSince Christopher's death, his wife
OL,12,FFiona Hall has campaigned for better
OL,13,Ftree maintenance and has recently
OL,14,Fenlisted the help of arboriculture
OL,15,Fexpert, Alex Cannon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
