OL,3,CTrees in need of 'urgent attention' in
OL,4,Cpark where man was killed
OL,6,FMr Cannon has now carried out a survey
OL,7,Fand says six trees in the same park
OL,8,Fare in need of semi-urgent attention
OL,9,Fin the next three months, with three
OL,10,Fof those needing to be cut down
OL,11,Fcompletely to make them safe.
OL,13,FOne other tree and a stump should also
OL,14,Fbe looked at in the next six months,
OL,15,Faccording to the survey.
OL,17,FFiona says the report findings are
OL,18,Fdeeply troubling: "I'm really, really
OL,19,Fworried. I've been sleepless since
OL,20,FI've seen is report."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
