OL,6,F"I can sit here, quite comfortably and
OL,7,Fsay the things that should be being
OL,8,Fdone, are not being done and people
OL,9,Fare still going to lose their lives."
OL,11,FCheshire East Council was fined
OL,12,F#500,000 in November 2024 after an
OL,13,Finvestigation by the Health and Safety
OL,14,FExecutive (HSE) found that no
OL,15,Finvestigation was carried out to
OL,16,Fassess whether the tree that killed
OL,17,FChristopher posed a future safety risk.
OL,19,FA judge at Chester Magistrates' Court
OL,20,Fsaid the previous incident should have
OL,21,Facted "as a wake up call."
