OL,3,CTrees in need of 'urgent attention' in
OL,4,Cpark where man was killed
OL,6,FFiona Hall, who has launched a
OL,7,Fpetition calling for mandatory tree
OL,8,Fmaintenance in public places, said the
OL,9,Fincident had "obliterated everything."
OL,11,FShe said: "It just robbed him of his
OL,12,Flife in a heartbeat, simply walking
OL,13,Fyour dog in the most avoidable wholly
OL,14,Favoidable situation known to man."
OL,16,FThe HSE said the council, which
OL,17,Fmanaged the park, did not have a
OL,18,Fformal, overarching strategy to manage
OL,19,Fthe risks from trees in public areas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
