OL,6,FIt added that the authority's grounds
OL,7,Fservices contractor, Ansa
OL,8,FEnvironmental Services Ltd, also had
OL,9,Fno robust tree management policy.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Cheshire East
OL,12,FCouncil said: "The safety of everyone
OL,13,Fwho visits and enjoys our parks and
OL,14,Fopen spaces is our highest priority.
