OL,6,F"Since the tragic death of Mr Hall, we
OL,7,Fhave introduced a number of
OL,8,Fimprovements under our adopted tree
OL,9,Fmanagement strategy to strengthen
OL,10,Fsafety measures. This includes routine
OL,11,Fcyclical tree inspections and risk
OL,12,Fassessments by professionally
OL,13,Fqualified arboriculturists, and timely
OL,14,Fcompletion of works.
OL,16,F"We received Mrs Hall's report on The
OL,17,FCarrs earlier this week and will
OL,18,Freview its contents at a meeting on
OL,19,FMonday with all relevant council
OL,20,Fofficers present."
